# SIPHS-CHV/COMETA Corpus v1.01

This corpus is released with a CC BY-ND-NC license (http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/). 

Please note that the official latest version of SIPHS-CHV/COMETA can be obtained only through www.siphs.org or by contacting Prof. Nigel Collier (nhc30@cam.ac.uk). If you obtain SIPHS-CHV/COMETA elsewhere, the authors do not guarantee for the accuracy for the contents, which may be outdated.

This file, along with LICENSE, is integral part of the SIPHS-CHV/COMETA distribution and **must** be included with the corpus.

If you believe that SIPHS-CHV/COMETA contain content you own and you want it removed, please contact Prof. Nigel Collier (nhc30@cam.ac.uk) or follow the instruction on https://siphs.org/corpus and we will process your request as soon as possible. Please provide your Reddit username and the URL of the post with your request for verification purposes. 

If you use SIPHS-CHV/COMETA in your work, please cite:

@inproceedings{basaldella-2020-cometa,
    title = "{COMETA}: A Corpus for Medical Entity Linking in the Social Media",
    author = "Basaldella, Marco  and Liu, Fangyu, and Shareghi, Ehsan, and Collier, Nigel",
    booktitle = "Proceedings of the 2020 Conference on Empirical Methods in Natural Language Processing",
    month = nov,
    year = "2020",
    publisher = "Association for Computational Linguistics"
}

## Anonymisation Notes

For anonymisation purposes, certain dates and username have been anonymised following these rules:
- Dates (in the dd/mm/yyyy format or similar) have been replaced with $DATE.
- Months have been replaced with $MONTH.
- Years have been replaced with $YEAR.
- Usernames have been replaced with $USER.